						<p><hi rend="bold">Kōṉēriṉmaikoṇḍāṉ: No date.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription in two pieces is damaged and does not seem to be complete.</p>						

						<p>It appears to record the gift of money to provide oil for some lamps given to the temple at Koḻumam.</p>						

